defs.name: Error
defs.value:
pub enum Error {

    #[fail(display = "{:?}", _0)]
    Codes(HashSet<Code>),

    #[fail(display = "{}", _0)]
    Reqwest(
            #[cause]
            reqwest::Error),

    #[fail(display = "{}", _0)]
    Io(
       #[cause]
       io::Error),
}

pub enum Code {

    InvalidSecret,
    MissingResponse,
    InvalidResponse,
    BadRequest,
    Unknown(String),
}
